  1. Do ratings depend on the cacao percentage of a chocolate bar? Create both numerical and graphical summaries, and explain. Now, we are ready to explore.
summary(choco$Cocoa_Percent)
##    Min. 1st Qu.  Median    Mean 3rd Qu.    Max. 
##   42.00   70.00   70.00   71.65   75.00  100.00
plot(choco$Cocoa_Percent, choco$Rating,
     main = "Scatterplot of Cocoa Percent",
     xlab = "Cocoa percent",
     ylab = "Rating")

barplot(table(choco$Cocoa_Percent), 
        main = "Barchart of Cocoa_Percent",
        xlab = "Cocoa percent",
        ylab = "Rating")
